    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104410/extras/06f6c74a6ccaba13771ac4629b5b0bbb.avif?t=1772159870\" width=1600 height=900 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104410/extras/c059b9644eda88b8d8abe80f0ecab76e.avif?t=1772159870\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104410/extras_big/c059b9644eda88b8d8abe80f0ecab76e.avif?t=1772159870 width=800 height=116 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ΔσμΔ // 想了解《矩阵：零日危机》更多游戏资讯，请关注官方微信公众号「矩阵零日危机」或关注 bilibili 官方账号 @矩阵零日危机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >======================================================================</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《矩阵：零日危机》是一款融合了虚拟多元世界题材的合作射击PVE端游。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将永远不会进入同一场战斗，在单局中构筑多样战斗流派，在随机关卡组队与极具挑战性的BOSS共斗，在激烈的枪林弹雨中选择你的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索多元风格世界，驾驭不同职业英雄，成就属于你的道路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请记住，死亡不是你的终点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104410/extras/a9781c6dfba198be20308d140f537fd5.avif?t=1772159870\" width=1080 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不同英雄角色拥有风格各异的“技能动作化”设计，玩家可以化身暗中突袭的近战刺客、也可以成为灵活游走的双枪游侠、或是成为极限输出的狂暴战士。施放技能连击，打出华丽combo，让你在战斗中体验子弹风暴与技能特效交织的爽快割草感！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104410/extras/a96d184bcdd45a3fb2bd4be2ee9e9348.avif?t=1772159870\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104410/extras_big/a96d184bcdd45a3fb2bd4be2ee9e9348.avif?t=1772159870 width=1600 height=900 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104410/extras/b97644d34d98191030f2e1d83af71a44.avif?t=1772159870\" width=1080 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家可在战斗中自由选择极具深度的肉鸽特色增益“八大法则之力”，组合出上百种增益效果，为英雄解锁更多打法流派。每一次选择都是战局的重构，每一场战斗皆是策略的涅槃。自定义你的构筑玩法，成为战局的主宰者！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104410/extras/10351991e02a584307a6789e3bc4edc8.avif?t=1772159870\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104410/extras_big/10351991e02a584307a6789e3bc4edc8.avif?t=1772159870 width=1600 height=900 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104410/extras/2763b1ebc236e075dc4391a394e3f44b.avif?t=1772159870\" width=1080 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >海量局外能力模块×策略矩阵系统​​，构筑你的专属战斗宇宙。​​你可以随心所欲地搭配拼装，从锋芒攻击到钢铁防御，再到奇妙特技，​​每一次选择都在塑造独一无二的成长路线​​。深度满足刷宝与养成的双重乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104410/extras/089aee557da036a1d9b918ee47cdae13.avif?t=1772159870\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104410/extras_big/089aee557da036a1d9b918ee47cdae13.avif?t=1772159870 width=1600 height=900 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104410/extras/e1c556783673ad9abad72e4687270f91.avif?t=1772159870\" width=1080 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BOSS难度平衡性优化，局内玩家可以灵活运用精心构筑的流派，与多重战斗策略完美共振，打出极致刷图效果。更可与队友并肩作战，合斗强敌，碰撞出加倍的战斗惊喜与策略火花！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104410/extras/84b9cebd01856850a2c6117fae61e2ff.avif?t=1772159870\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104410/extras_big/84b9cebd01856850a2c6117fae61e2ff.avif?t=1772159870 width=1600 height=900 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u> </u></strong></p>",
